company.description:
CREANGEL is a Colombian company that specializes in developing and deploying applications based on search of structured and unstructured information, as well as recognition of images to text (OCR). This means that we use advanced technology to help organizations process large amounts of data and find the information they need quickly and easily.
One of the key technologies that we use to help our clients is Solr, an open-source search platform that allows us to build custom search applications tailored to each client's unique needs. Solr is highly flexible and can be used to index and search a wide variety of data types, including text, images, and videos. We use Solr to help our clients find the information they need quickly and easily, whether it's buried in a massive database or hidden in unstructured data sources like file servers  or email inboxes.
Our team od developers and analysts can help organizations uncover insights and patterns in their data, which can be used to make better business decisions and improve performance. We work with clients to develop custom analytics solutions that are tailored to their specific needs, using tools like Druid, Spark, and other big data technologies.
Overall, our goal at CREANGEL is to help organizations of all sizes and industries make the most of their data. Whether you're looking to improve operational efficiency, uncover new business opportunities, or simply gain a better understanding of your customers, we can help. Contact us today to learn more about our services and how we can help your organization succeed.
